Class DetailedSimulationView

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iha.emulator.ui.simulations.detailed.DetailedSimulationView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DetailedSimulationPresenter.Display, javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class DetailedSimulationView
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, DetailedSimulationPresenter.Display
    Class providing GUI components for "Detailed simulation". Part View of MVP design pattern. Contains methods invoked on user interaction with user interface. These methods call appropriate presenter method to process user interaction.
    Author:
    Filip Sutovsky
